>Soojin</a>于昨天（10 月 25 日）发布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-gi-dle-soojin-cryptic-teaser-solo-debut-black-forest-3521062">了一段神秘的“黑森林”视频，预告了她期待已久的个人首秀</a>。在远离公众视线两年后，这位歌手还开设了新的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/brd_soojinofficial/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@SOOJIN.OFFICIAL" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>账户。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/meghan-trainor-obsessed-with-gi-dle-after-working-with-them-3521599">梅根·特雷纳 (Meghan Trainor) 表示，在与 (G)I-DLE 合作后，她对他们“着迷”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
